{"id":"d78e94ff-8ff7-46a8-a958-e04200a557ee","name":"~Aria~","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(100, 187, 250)\"><strong><em>You have a nice couple days off in the beautiful Kanto region and choose to visit the local onsen and spa resort close to your house. however you find an anthropomorphic Vaporeon, that’s currently occupying the steaming bath. </em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">✶══════════════════✶</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>This bot is a re-release of my closest friend Crunch’s Aria Bot with only a scenario change </strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">✶══════════════════✶</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>This is an Official bot and Art &amp; Character are owned by Rilex Lenov please go support them on Patreon</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>✶══════════════════✶</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>✶</strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"><strong>Check out my other bots</strong></span><strong>✶</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/d38e50c3-e165-4652-ac00-e5a723740a56_character-hera\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Hera</strong></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(129, 189, 221)\"><strong><em>You reach your local Coffee shop to get a good meal and a drink, and you see a cute looking luxray gal noticing that her card declines for her usual drink. Will you help her out and start an electrifying new friendship?</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-j0re88 css-4g6ai3\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 305px; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/645180de-1c7f-4144-b2df-cc69def4ef77_d8235d83-1cbd-42c0-8cbb-c05ddabbfa00.webp?width=1000\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>✶══════════════════✶</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/2985a878-08df-4cf1-9eb0-1d7e6c2fcb03_character-midori-solo\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>Midori (SOLO)</em></strong></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(106, 211, 114)\"><strong><em>You decide to take a shortcut through an alley after a long day at work. But when you turn around, you see the aftermath of a street fight, as bunch of defeated dudes on the ground and a slightly hurt Gardevoir. Will you help us her out and get her somewhere safe?</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-j0re88 css-4g6ai3\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 305px; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/645180de-1c7f-4144-b2df-cc69def4ef77_afeafd0b-d4f4-4cf6-a059-00c2b2ba895a.webp?width=1000\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>✶══════════════════✶</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/430b0227-c075-4dff-9e53-a59477b39a43_character-laurel\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>Laurel</em></strong></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(20, 186, 76)\"><strong><em>You get a text from your close friend Laurel asking if you’d want to hang out at her place. You happily agree and make your way to her house that sits in a lovely forest, away from the chaotic city.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: ","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"645180de-1c7f-4144-b2df-cc69def4ef77_76702442-efb6-483b-b94d-4408561950e0.webp","creator":"Jupiter The Cat","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","🦄 Non-human","🐙 Pokemon","👤 AnyPOV","🐺 Furry","🌗 Switch"],"chats":1456,"messages":24413,"created_at":"2024-10-09T22:51:14.875159+00:00"}